The Chronicle Bongani Ndlovu, Chronicle Reporter PRESIDENT Mnangagwa has announced that Vice President Dr Constantino Chiwenga has tied the knot with his partner Colonel Miniyothabo Baloyi. <img class="size-medium wp-image-598789" src="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/04/Vice-President-Dr-Constantino-Chiwenga-360x201.jpg" alt="" width="360" height="201" srcset="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/04/Vice-President-Dr-Constantino-Chiwenga-360x200.jpg 360w, https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/04/Vice-President-Dr-Constantino-Chiwenga.jpg 680w" sizes="(max-width: 360px) 100vw, 360px" /> Vice-President Constantino Chiwenga In a statement yesterday, the Chief Secretary to the President and Cabinet, Dr Misheck Sibanda said the President wishes the couple well in their marriage. “His Excellency the President, Dr E. D. Mnangagwa, wishes to inform the Nation that Honourable Vice President, General (Retired) Dr CDGN Chiwenga, has tied the knot with his partner, Colonel Miniyothabo Baloyi. <img class="wp-image-471336 size-full" src="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2019/10/Dr-Misheck-Sibanda-1-680x380-2.png" alt="" width="680" height="380" srcset="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2019/10/Dr-Misheck-Sibanda-1-680x380-2.png 680w, https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2019/10/Dr-Misheck-Sibanda-1-680x380-2-360x200.png 360w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" /> Dr Misheck Sibanda “Col Baloyi is a serving Officer in the Zimbabwe National Army, ZNA. The President, the First Lady, Amai Auxillia Mnangagwa (Dr), and the First Family wish the couple a lifelong partnership full of love and affection,” reads the statement. 